description:
&lt;p&gt;Exciting opportunity for a recently or newly qualified Band 5 Speech and Language Therapist to work alongside more experienced Speech &amp; Language Therapists in providing a specialised service to patients with acquired neurological communication and swallowing problems in a Community setting. this is a permanent, part time position at 15 hours per week. There are fabulous opportunities for professional development and support from the experienced Adult Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To provide assessment, diagnosis, treatment planning and appropriate intervention, including discharge, for adults with communication and / or swallowing difficulties so as to achieve optimum potential for each individual.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To develop and monitor appropriate therapy programmes from a range of options&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To provide specialised advice to relatives and other health professionals to optimise the communication environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To continually process patient responses and continuously make fine adjustments to interactions and treatment programmes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To provide ongoing training and support for other involved professionals to enable them to implement agreed intervention targets and strategies as appropriate to the caseload&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To offer advice, support and resources to families and carers to enable them to be actively involved in the therapy programme.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To provide training, supervision and support for Speech and Language Therapy Assistants, volunteers and others involved in the treatment and/or care of adults on the caseload&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please refer to the Job Description and Person Specification for all essential and desirable criteria required for the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is for 15 Hours/Week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Jane Giles Job title Head of Service: Speech &amp; Language Therapy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email addressjane.giles6@nhs.net Telephone number0191 2823085&lt;/p&gt;
